<plot>This is the (almost true) story of how young Ginger got into the adult business and lived through it. She first meets a sleazy agent, who only sends models out on job interviews if he takes them to "lunch" first. Happy Harry Reems gives anxious "Ginger" her name when they meet on her first job. From then on, it's Ginger bar the door. She is off in a business that can turn mere mortals into stars, in Ginger's case, she has a gift that puts her above the rest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?215183</url></doc>
